Configuration Fields for Each Action Type:

**Lead Data Actions:**
- update_lead_score: { score: number, reason: string }
- add_lead_tag: { tag: string }
- remove_lead_tag: { tag: string }
- add_to_funnel: { funnelId: string, stageId: string }
- move_to_funnel_stage: { funnelId: string, stageId: string }
- remove_from_funnel: { funnelId: string }
- update_lead_field: { field: string, value: any }
- create_deal: { dealName: string, amount: number, stage: string }

**Communication Actions:**
- send_whatsapp_message: { message: string, templateId: string }
- create_email_message: { subject: string, body: string, templateId: string }
- send_internal_notification: { message: string, recipients: string[] }
- send_push_notification: { title: string, body: string, data: object }
- schedule_drip_sequence: { sequenceId: string, delay: number }

**Task & Workflow Actions:**
- create_task: { title: string, description: string, assignee: string, dueDate: string }
- create_calendar_event: { title: string, startTime: string, endTime: string, attendees: string[] }
- add_note_to_lead: { note: string, noteType: string }
- add_followup_date: { followupDate: string, notes: string }

**Zoom Integration Actions:**
- create_zoom_meeting: { topic: string, startTime: string, duration: number, attendees: string[] }

**Payment Actions:**
- create_invoice: { amount: string, description: string, dueDate: string }
- issue_refund: { amount: number, reason: string, paymentId: string }

**System Actions:**
- call_webhook: { url: string, method: string, headers: object, payload: object }
- trigger_another_automation: { automationRuleId: string, delay: number }
